title: Garmin MapSource Baltic State Roads (BSR) v1
description:
Garmin MapSource Baltic States Roads (BSR) v1

Product homepage: <a href="
http://www.garmin.lt/en/disp.php/lt_products/lt_cartography/lt_cartography_road/lt_cartography_road/2913" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.garmin.lt/en/disp.php/lt_products/lt_cartography/lt_cartography_road/lt_cartography_road/2913</a>

BSR (Baltic States Roads) is a routable (!) map of all Baltic countries
(Lithuania, Latvia and Estonia) for GARMIN GPS navigators. It contains
motorways, county and residential roads, with street level detailed maps
of every town and city. Total road/street network included contain over
200000km. Other objects includes lakes, rivers, railway lines. Will
automatically create point-to-point routes on compatible GARMIN GPS,
with further turn-by-turn navigation directions. Includes turn
restrictions and one way street information. It is a "locked" product.
Some discount, ussually -10%, will be granted for the second and further
units.

Unlock Codes for PC:
KE8A2-X6YRD-XALUN-9CHW6-N8DMF
Z9G94-LKUEY-CLGHK-BP4D5-YA7P4

Original gmapsupp.img and (non-original) MapSource version included.
